  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Solithromycin in the Treatment of Nonalcoholic Steatohepatitis Without Cirrhosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label, Proof of Principle Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Solithromycin for the Treatment of Nonalcoholic Steatohepatitis Without Cirrhosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
