  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effects of solithromycin on hepatic histology
      and biomarkers in patients with nonalcoholic steatohepatitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients will be administered solithromycin for 13 weeks with regular safety visits and liver
      biopsies at baseline and after treatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
